  "original_title": "\u0d91\u0db1\u0dca\u0da2\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0ddd \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0da2\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A section of engine drivers also joins the strike",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Indika Dodangoda, the convenor of the train hoisting trade union, said tonight that a part of the locomotive drivers' union will join the strike of railway station workers and controllers from midnight today (5).",
        "Mr. Dodangoda further said that the locomotive drivers union, which supports the train hoisting union, will join the strike and the railway workers are facing the fuel problem."
      ],
